%p
  要搜尋的關鍵字。（標點符號會被去除，包括半形小括號）
%p 
  也可使用
  =link_to 'Extended 語法', controller: 'static_pages', action: 'search_extended'
  。例如：
%ul
  %li
    AND:
    =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="法鼓" "迦葉"'
  %li
    OR:
    =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="法鼓" | "迦葉"'
  %li
    NOT:
    =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="迦葉" !"迦葉佛"'
  %li
    NEAR:
    %ul
      %li
        =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="法鼓" NEAR/7 "迦葉"'
        (NEAR/ 後面的數字 表示兩個關鍵詞中間的距離)
      %li
        NEAR 多個詞:
        =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="老子" NEAR/7 "道" NEAR/3 "經"'
  %li
    Exclude
    %ul
      %li
        排除前搭配
        =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="直心" -"正直心"'
      %li
        排除後搭配
        =link_to_url '/search/all_in_one?q="舍利" -"舍利弗"'
%p 關鍵字詞中若含：單引號、雙引號、半形減號，需 escape，例如：
%ul
  %li
    搜尋 samantato AND 'nantanāvāptiśāsani
    =link_to_url %q(/search/all_in_one?q="samantato" "\%27nantanāvāptiśāsani")
  %li
    搜尋 Your AND "mang-kun"
    =link_to_url %q(/search/all_in_one?q="Your" "\"mang\-kun\"")
